review: ***** *** ** *** **** ******** * **** **** **** She's so friendly and professional. The way she handles her patient is marvellous. I am a very hygiene concerned person and her clinic met my requirements. I didn't felt a single thing while she was treating me. More importantly, she makes sure that her patient knows and understands the reason behind every step. No doctor ever tell me about the thyroid collar but she did. Her fees is affordable and there is some sense of calmness that comes along with treatment which is mainly required especially when you're getting treated by a dentist. I am looking forward to get treated by her.
